  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK661">
<l>viṉaittiṭpa meṉpa toruvaṉmaṉattiṭpa </l>
<l> maṟṟavai yellām piṟa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Firmness in action is (simply) one's firmness of mind; all other (abilities) are not of this nature.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
